        <briefdescription>
<para>Value of the Response Code field. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The following response codes are accepted:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1ae6e8ebcfc2578eefec11cb9e8222eafd" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_SUCCESS</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1a96278dcde41d37b6e9fd2a926c9ff16a" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_CAP_UNSUPPORTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1a5a0230629bffc7659ec8127169a90b62" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_CONF_UNSUPPORTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1af587ec0a8b72fd9a7379aa173a8beb21" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_CONF_REJECTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1ad604f01d7a964fc8ae55dc76a5a8e0a7" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_METADATA_UNSUPPORTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1a9945d6001d365d759023fc233514ed06" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_METADATA_REJECTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1a9676a2e7fc5e417cbae2cea663204ccb" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_NO_MEM</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1ac6c03bd8827040ce48905c58ea7d423a" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_UNSPECIFIED</ref> </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
