        <briefdescription>
<para>Response metadata type. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If the Response Code is one of the following:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1ad604f01d7a964fc8ae55dc76a5a8e0a7" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_METADATA_UNSUPPORTED</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="group__bt__bap_1gga9f7efa749c75edd32dc50503397ab9d1a9945d6001d365d759023fc233514ed06" kindref="member">BT_BAP_ASCS_RSP_CODE_METADATA_REJECTED</ref> the value of the Metadata Type shall be used. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
